flowchart LR
    Client([Client])
    CDN[CDN Edge<br/>cached 301]
    API[App Server<br/>shorten / redirect]
    IDSvc[ID Service<br/>Snowflake + base62]
    Cache[(KV Cache<br/>alias to long_url)]
    Store[(Alias Store<br/>wide-column)]
    Stream[(Click Event Stream)]
    Warehouse[(Analytics Warehouse)]

    Client -->|shorten| API
    API -->|generate alias| IDSvc
    API -->|write| Store
    API -->|warm| Cache

    Client -->|GET short.ly/abc| CDN
    CDN -->|miss| API
    API -->|lookup| Cache
    Cache -->|miss| Store
    API -->|301 redirect| Client
    API -.->|fire-and-forget click| Stream
    Stream -.->|ingest| Warehouse

    classDef external fill:#1e2533,stroke:#3a4a6e,color:#cfd6e6
    classDef service fill:#1a3a2e,stroke:#3a6e54,color:#cfe6d6
    classDef store fill:#1e2a3e,stroke:#3a5a8e,color:#cfdcef
    classDef config fill:#3a2e1a,stroke:#6e5a3a,color:#efdfcf

    class Client external
    class CDN,API,IDSvc service
    class Cache,Store,Stream,Warehouse store
